headline: CMS Energy (CMS) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: CMS Energy (CMS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +1.28% and +5.92%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
